3. Geo data
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   3-1. geo-countries
      - All data is licensed under the Open Data Commons Public Domain Dedication and License.
      - https://github.com/datasets/geo-countries

   3-2. Administrative divisions
      - Public Domain (Natural Earth)
      - https://github.com/nvkelso/natural-earth-vector
      - Source: ne_10m_admin_1_states_provinces.geojson

   3-3. Natural Earth (International Date Line)
      - Public Domain
      - https://www.naturalearthdata.com/
      - Source: ne_110m_geographic_lines

   3-4. Japan Old Provinces
      - License: CC BY-NC (specific version not indicated by the provider;
        see https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/ for the license family)
      - Credit (as specified by the provider):
        人間文化研究機構, https://www.bridge.nihu.jp/researchdata/file/18045150
        (National Institutes for the Humanities (NIHU),
        https://www.bridge.nihu.jp/researchdata/file/18045150)
      - Title: "Bakumatsu-Meiji Boundary Data" (幕末明治地勢地図境界データ)
      - Commercial use: not permitted without prior consultation with the provider
      - Converted from SHP to GeoJSON using GDAL/ogr2ogr (a build-time tool only;
        no GDAL code is redistributed in this repository) - https://gdal.org
      - Simplified using Mapshaper (a build-time tool only; not redistributed) -
        https://mapshaper.org
      - Coordinates rounded to 6 decimal places
